snippet.title: Jeff Jones
snippet.description:
I’m Jeff Jones and welcome to my Channel. 

On my Channel, I’m going to talk about a variety of topics that I’m interested in like politics, sport and current news as well as some of the personal stories from my life experiences. I was also hoping to do some interviews with different people around Cork and Ireland to allow them to share their stories and ideas.

If you want to keep up with what’s going on on this channel; subscribe and make a comment if you have an idea for a video that you think I should do.
